channel.title: Help with model adding, please?(maybe very simple!)
channel.description: i'm using thee underground client and source and was wondering how to add models. i tryed to add the staff capes and those but they didn't work! instead of getting the items i wanted i found out that almost all 8000-15000 models are some stupid dwarf heads named null...is it possible to add a model over or under 8000-15000 and is it advisable (heard it could cause big torment to the client!)

item.title: Help with model adding, please?(maybe very simple!)
item.dc:creator: @dylan_0789 dylan_0789
item.description:
@dylan_0789 wrote:

you can basically add any model id ranged 1-15,000.
after u add them, type “add model #####” for each model.
